text:
Today I came to try the Roast Pork stall here.  The tenderness and juiciness of the Roast Pork and Char Siew just melts in your mouth.

You still get the crisp char taste after biting into the meat!

You have many soup choices here too!

This is a special mention of the economic rice stall. I may look like a delivery rider but I am not. I could sense that the server gave me extra portions of food without charging me extra due to his kindness and empathy. I am giving him a good review to thank him for his kind act.

New Zhi char taste better than the old one IMO worth the try.

Roasted rice store is really good worth the money if you like sweet sauce.
Ordered Zi Char curry fish head $26. Only half fish head without much vegetables added inside seems too expensive. Only a few lady fingers, eggplant and cabbage very miserable.

Good cantonese style roast meats stall, also  serving  relatively good Wanton noodles as well. Economical mixed rice stall with good variety of dishes, average prices. Che Zhar stall serves the usual fair of average standard.

2nd October 2023: Currently closed due to change of ownership. Scheduled to reopen in November.
